      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy tests on canonical flows must confirm theoretical convergence rates for all relevant solver modules.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy verification performed only on laminar pipe flow benchmark. Turbulence model and non-Newtonian viscosity modules lack independent code verification at the required level."
    },
