      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments must span the full COU operating envelope (all five flow-speed combinations) under VAD-representative conditions.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments cover three of five required operating points. The two highest-speed conditions relevant to peak VAD demand are not represented in the available experimental dataset."
