      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity of hemolysis prediction to turbulence model and power-law exponent in hemolysis damage model must be quantified through systematic model-form uncertainty study.",
      "rationale": "Single turbulence model (SST k-omega) and single hemolysis model exponent used throughout. Model-form sensitivity analysis not performed. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
