      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full probabilistic characterisation of all model inputs including geometric tolerances, fluid properties, and operating condition variability must be provided for Monte Carlo UQ.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed on flow rate and rotational speed only. Geometric manufacturing tolerances and blood rheology variability not included in the uncertainty propagation. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
