      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size must be sufficient to characterise inter-sample variability; statistical power analysis required at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump dataset uses a single physical pump specimen. Inter-specimen variability in hemolysis performance not characterised. No statistical power analysis available. Epistemic gap at MRL 5."
