    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors were formally assessed; in all seven cases the achieved credibility level falls below the required level for MRL 5. Six factors were not assessed and represent unresolved epistemic gaps. The overall credibility package does not meet the minimum requirements for regulatory submission of a Class III VAD device. Decision: Not accepted pending remediation of identified gaps. Package integrity hash recorded; digital signature pending completion of the authorised signing workflow.",
